            <div class="tiny-slide client-testi text-center">
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">After adopting NocoBase, the time we spend on administrative tasks dropped by 50%, collaboration and communication improved, and our recruitment process became faster and more efficient.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">At TEDxDUTH, we believe innovation and collaboration can change the world. NocoBase helps us streamline daily operations so we can focus more energy on what truly matters: creating inspiring events and spreading meaningful ideas.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">If your organization is dealing with chaotic or inefficient workflows, NocoBase is not just a tool. It is a comprehensive solution that unlocks your team's potential and makes more possible. For us, NocoBase has been a true game changer: it has empowered us to dream bigger, transformed how we work, and continues to shape our community.</p>
              <p class="text-muted fst-italic">We are grateful to NocoBase for being an indispensable partner on our journey. Together, we keep advancing innovation and the spread of ideas.</p>
